  <article>
    <h1>Free First Consultation</h1>
    <p>I offer a free initial Skype consultation (typically 30-45 minutes) to discuss your symptoms, diagnose whether focal hand dystonia retrainable triggers are present, and evaluate if my approach is a good fit for you.</p>
    
    <p>During this session, we will look at how your hand behaves on the instrument, talk about your history, and outline potential next steps without any financial commitment.</p>

    <blockquote>
      "An initial discussion is critical to understand the specific movement triggers and ensure a retrainable pathway is available."
    </blockquote>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn">Book Your Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </article>
